      <title>拜登同意在协议中禁止美国大使馆悬挂 LGBTQ 骄傲旗帜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/lgbtq-pride-flags-banned-at-us-embassies-in-1-2t-spending-plan-backed-by-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登同意禁止美国大使馆悬挂 LGBTQ 骄傲旗帜，这是一项 1.2 万亿美元支出协议的一部分，该协议旨在让大多数美国政府机构在 9 月 30 日之前保持开放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/lgbtq-pride-flags-banned-at-us-embassies-in-1-2t-spending-plan-backed-by-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国极右翼在叛乱党的抵抗中失去支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/german-far-right-loses-support-amid-resistance-insurgent-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国极右翼选择党在全国范围内失去了支持，因为它面临公众的抵制和一个专注于批评移民以及该国对乌克兰战争努力的支持的叛乱政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/german-far-right-loses-support-amid-resistance-insurgent-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国投票反对批准欧盟-加拿大自由贸易协定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/france-votes-against-ratifying-eu-canada-free-trade-agreement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国参议院投票反对批准欧盟与加拿大的自由贸易协定，这对法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙来说是一个政治挫折，意味着该协定将仅暂时有效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/france-votes-against-ratifying-eu-canada-free-trade-agreement</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:18:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新的保守党叛逃表明苏纳克失去了对约翰逊联盟的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/new-tory-defection-shows-sunak-losing-grip-on-johnson-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大曼彻斯特的保守党市长候选人叛逃到新兴的改革英国党，这是英国首相里希·苏纳克在上届大选中对保守党获胜至关重要的领域失去支持的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/new-tory-defection-shows-sunak-losing-grip-on-johnson-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:15:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳反 LGBTQ 法案引发争议，部长任命陷入停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/row-over-ghana-s-anti-lgbtq-bill-stalls-appointment-of-ministers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳议会正在推迟批准新内阁部长，以向总统纳纳·阿库福-阿多施压，要求其就一项反 LGBTQ 法案做出决定，该法案需要他的同意才能成为法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/row-over-ghana-s-anti-lgbtq-bill-stalls-appointment-of-ministers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:14:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>APS 称阿尔及利亚将于 9 月 7 日举行总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/algeria-to-hold-presidential-elections-on-sept-7-aps-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国营 APS 通讯社援引现任总统阿卜杜勒马吉德·特布恩 (Abdelmadjid Tebboune) 的决定称，阿尔及利亚将于 9 月 7 日“提前”举行总统选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/algeria-to-hold-presidential-elections-on-sept-7-aps-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:09:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大计划三年内将临时居民人数减少 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/canada-plans-to-cut-temporary-residents-by-20-over-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大这个严重依赖移民作为经济驱动力的国家，在移民涌入加剧了住房短缺之后，正在缩减其雄心壮志，计划减少临时居民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/canada-plans-to-cut-temporary-residents-by-20-over-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:06:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度被指控密谋反对的锡克教分裂分子是谁？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/sikh-separatism-explained-who-are-the-activists-india-is-accused-of-targeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国检察官指控印度政府特工策划暗杀一名寻求独立锡克教国家的锡克教美国公民。这一阴谋在纽约遭到挫败。但大约在同一时间，潜在受害者的一名同伙在不列颠哥伦比亚省被杀，促使加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多公开指责印度参与其中，而印度则予以强烈否认。印度对美国指控的调查发现，流氓特工并未授权]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/sikh-separatism-explained-who-are-the-activists-india-is-accused-of-targeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:04:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
